modName: Sandor Clegane - The Hound Playable Character
descriptionHtml:
For my first and hopefully not my last mod Ive attempted to create The Hounds face from Game of Thrones to play in the world of Skyrim as he is just pure badass motherfuckery... This is still a work in progress and the template will be updated, yes i am aware that it doesnt look exactly like him but it will be updated. feedback would be appreciated as to help me make this better. Thanks and enjoy !

Note this mod requires:
-Race Menu
-SKSE
IT WILL NOT WORK IF YOU DONT HAVE THESE INSTALLED AS OF CUSTOM TEXTURES THESE MODS PROVIDE
author: The Migmonster
